      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Just saw that [this page](https://mithro-gf180mcu-pdk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/physical_verification/design_manual/drm_15.html) of the PDK mentions a p-well resistor alongside the n-well resistor. I couldn't find the schematic symbol or model by grepping inside the tech, so I'm curious if there actually is one.\n\n-- Not actually planning on using them, I'm just curious.",
