      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Unfortunately, I don't think it is part of the PDK.\n\nThe resistors page does not list it: https://gf180mcu-pdk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/analog/model_parameters/LV/LV_1_4_4.html\n\nLooking at the spice models in the PDK (`sm141064.spice`), I can see that they only include the ones shown on the resistors page.\n\nMagic, however, does extract resistance for pwell/isosub during pex.",
